260
00:17:29,980 --> 00:17:32,280
-Qu’est-ce que c’est ?
-De la magie.

261
00:17:32,410 --> 00:17:34,480
Très puissante.

262
00:17:35,080 --> 00:17:36,820
Regarde.

263
00:17:36,920 --> 00:17:39,120
Tu verras ce que j’ai vu.

264
00:17:39,220 --> 00:17:41,660
Tu ressentiras ce que j’ai ressenti.

265
00:17:50,530 --> 00:17:52,300
