268
00:18:11,750 --> 00:18:12,850
Quoi ?

269
00:18:14,690 --> 00:18:16,290
Tu ressors ?

270
00:18:17,360 --> 00:18:19,460
Je fais une réunion {\i1}tuperware.

271
00:18:19,730 --> 00:18:21,460
