431
00:29:04,410 --> 00:29:06,780
Il avait qu’à lui dire de se retenir.

432
00:29:10,850 --> 00:29:12,810
Servez moi un double.

433
00:29:13,650 --> 00:29:15,480
C’est un désastre.

434
00:29:16,250 --> 00:29:18,850
